  "@graph": [

    {
      "comment": "=== AGENTS & ROLES ===  Jane typed only as Person (cco:ont00001262) per JI-005a Q-O-3 / Onto Observation A from PR #10 review. Reasoner classifies her as TargetAnalyst (and thus IntelligenceAnalyst by inference) via the bearer-of-some-TargetAnalysisRole pattern. Direct typing as TargetAnalyst would make CQ-012's anti-rigidity test trivially pass."
    },
    {
      "@id": "ex:Analyst_Jane_001",
      "@type": ["cco:ont00001262", "owl:NamedIndividual"],
      "label": "Target Analyst Jane (typed as Person; reasoner-classified as TargetAnalyst via role)",
      "obo:RO_0000053": "ex:Role_TargetAnalysis_Jane_001",
      "obo:BFO_0000056": [
        "ex:Process_Phase1BDA_001",
