    {
      "comment": "=== Q-O-3 CLASSIFICATION-TEST INDIVIDUALS ===  Five untyped Process individuals (one per CA leaf class), typed ONLY as obo:BFO_0000015. Each has the input/output signature required by its target leaf's owl:equivalentClass body. The reasoner must classify each into the corresponding leaf class — that's what gives CQ-009 (positive classification) inferential teeth. Without these, CQ-009 reduces to a tautology (testing whether an asserted type is asserted). Test ICEs are separate from canonical-scenario ICEs to keep this test surface fully isolated."
    },
    {
      "@id": "ex:TestICE_Imagery_001",
      "@type": ["ex:PostStrikeImagery", "owl:NamedIndividual"],
      "label": "Test ICE — post-strike imagery (input for untyped Phase1 + MEA test individuals)"
    },
    {
      "@id": "ex:TestICE_Phase1Report_001",
      "@type": ["ex:Phase1BDAReport", "owl:NamedIndividual"],
      "label": "Test ICE — Phase I BDA Report (output of untyped Phase1; input of untyped Phase2)"
    },
    {
      "@id": "ex:TestICE_Phase2Report_001",
      "@type": ["ex:Phase2BDAReport", "owl:NamedIndividual"],
      "label": "Test ICE — Phase II BDA Report"
    },
    {
      "@id": "ex:TestICE_Phase3Report_001",
      "@type": ["ex:Phase3BDAReport", "owl:NamedIndividual"],
      "label": "Test ICE — Phase III BDA Report"
    },
    {
      "@id": "ex:TestICE_MEAReport_001",
      "@type": ["ex:MEAReport", "owl:NamedIndividual"],
      "label": "Test ICE — MEA Report"
    },
    {
      "@id": "ex:TestICE_RARReport_001",
      "@type": ["ex:RARReport", "owl:NamedIndividual"],
      "label": "Test ICE — RAR Report"
    },

    {
      "@id": "ex:TestProcess_UntypedPhase1_001",
      "@type": ["obo:BFO_0000015", "owl:NamedIndividual"],
      "label": "Untyped test process — should classify as Phase1BattleDamageAssessment via equivalentClass",
      "comment": "Q-O-3 classification-test individual #1. Has IntelligenceProduct input (PostStrikeImagery is a subclass) and Phase1BDAReport output. Reasoner must infer ex:Phase1BattleDamageAssessment via the leaf's owl:equivalentClass body.",
      "cco:ont00001921": "ex:TestICE_Imagery_001",
      "cco:ont00001986": "ex:TestICE_Phase1Report_001"
    },
    {
      "@id": "ex:TestProcess_UntypedPhase2_001",
